<p>In short, we respect your privacy and ask that you do the same to others that use the site.</p>

<p>We strongly recommend that you never give other people access to your password or publish personal details such as your real name, email address, phone numbers, or link to personal sites that may have these details. We also recommend that you use a different password to access your user ID on TWTD as using the same password on all your favourite sites may compromise your security.</p>

<p>Cookies are used to remember who you are from one page to the next. This is standard practice and enables you to log in and participate in the forums and other interactive features.</p>

<p>For security reasons we log your IP address and each page request made to the server. This data is only available to us and will not be passed on to a third party unless legally required to do so. We reserve the right to ban users and take appropriate action in the event of site abuse.</p>

